---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Projects | Brian Zater"
  description="Brian Zater's projects: Tree of Life Prison Outreach, Gun Buyback Initiative, and PURPOSE App. Community-focused initiatives for rehabilitation and public safety."
>
  <h1>Projects</h1>

  <section class="project-section">
    <h2>Tree of Life Prison Outreach</h2>
    <p>
      This initiative donates copies of Tree of Life to the South Carolina Department
      of Corrections, expanding access to structured reflection materials within
      correctional environments. The program aims to support rehabilitation and
      intentional planning for individuals preparing for reentry.
    </p>
    <p class="project-status">In development.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="project-section">
    <h2>Gun Buyback Initiative</h2>
    <p>
      A community-based initiative focused on prevention and public safety. The
      program provides a structured pathway for voluntary firearm surrender,
      supporting harm reduction and community wellbeing.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="project-section">
    <h2>PURPOSE App</h2>
    <p>
      PURPOSE is an AI-powered personal alignment platform that helps individuals
      discover meaningful career direction through structured self-assessment of
      interests, personality tendencies, skills, and values. It transforms insight
      into action by guiding users through measurable goal setting, time tracking,
      and thought awareness. The system synthesizes these elements into a
      personalized roadmap for building a disciplined, purpose-driven life.
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .project-section {
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
  }

  .project-section h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .project-status {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #555555;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
